---
import Card from "./ui/card.astro";
import Section from "./ui/section.astro";
---

<Section
  monoTitle="/ Connect everything"
  title="Wire Epistola in through the APIs you already own."
  description="Common Ground support ships out of the box today; other orchestrators are delivered via custom adapters while we expand the integration catalog."
  contentClass="space-y-10"
>
  <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
    <Card variant="subtle">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Common Ground ready</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--muted-text)]">
        Built-in alignment with Common Ground APIs keeps municipalities compliant without reinventing orchestration.
      </p>
    </Card>
    <Card variant="subtle">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Open REST API</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--muted-text)]">
        Every template, clause, and delivery endpoint is controllable via our documented REST interface, ready for any stack.
      </p>
    </Card>
    <Card variant="subtle">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Custom adapters</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--muted-text)]">
        We co-design integrations for the orchestrators on your roadmap—no prebuilt connectors yet, but expert services on call.
      </p>
    </Card>
  </div>
  <Card variant="outline" class="text-sm text-[var(--muted-text)]">
    <p class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-peach-paper-heading)]">Integration roadmap</p>
    <p class="mt-2">
      We're actively validating packaged connectors for leading municipal orchestrators. Until those land, teams can move
      forward using REST endpoints, event hooks, and service engagements tailored to their environment.
    </p>
  </Card>
</Section>
